                     <msItem xml:id="MS_Heb_f_44-part3-item1">
                        <locus from="26a" to="36b">Fol. 26</locus>
                        <title>הגדה, beg. with קדוש to<quote>הירדן יסוב לאחור</quote>
                        </title>
                        <note>followed by (<locus from="35b" to="36b">fol. 35b</locus>) a liturgy, beg.<quote type="beg">נבקעו שבעת עבי שמים</quote>;<locus from="36a" to="36b">fol. 36</locus>much obliterated.</note>
